data.description: This updated beauty, shows of pure pride of ownership! Super fancy tile work throughout. Granite counters, and so many amenities! This is a must see for those picky buyers. This home is a truly turnkey beauty, just bring your clothes! This wonderful property is located a stones throw from Sierra Del Rio golf course, and a very short distance from Elephant Butte Lake. Seller is Motivated!
